name: Beacon in Estrella
description: Located in an amenity-rich master-planned community, Beacon in Estrella offers single-family luxury homes in Goodyear, AZ, featuring Toll Brothers quality and craftsmanship and personalization opportunities.

homesites.name: Chapin Ranch
homesites.plan: Discover Limited-Time Savings on Select Homes*
homesites.overview: Impressive urban appointments. The Chapin's inviting covered entry and welcoming foyer hallway flow into the expansive great room, casual dining area, and desirable covered patio beyond. The well-designed gourmet kitchen is highlighted by a large center island with a breakfast bar, plenty of counter and cabinet space, and a generous pantry. The gracious primary bedroom suite is complete with an enormous walk-in closet and spa-like primary bath with a dual-sink vanity, large luxe shower, and private water closet. Secondary bedrooms feature roomy closets and access to two shared hall baths, one with a separate dual-sink vanity area. Additional highlights include a desirable office off the foyer and a centrally located laundry.
